narrative:
No non-compliant items identified during this inspection. 
This was a focused inspection limited to the female Cocker Spaniel (#0A01607813) and male Yorkshire Terrier
(#082*612*126) previously identified under section 2.40 (b)(2) during the 5/28/14 inspection.  These animals were
examined by a veterinarian.  Treatment plans had been developed and were currently being followed for each of the
animals.
 
The inspection and exit interview were conducted with the licensee.
